Text-Simplify

This module provides function for simplifying a string by removing whitespaces
from the start and the end and replacing each sequence of internal whitespaces
with a single space.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Text::Simplify

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Text-Simplify

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Text-Simplify

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Text-Simplify

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Text-Simplify/


